  <text>
      <body>         
         <pb n="1" facs= "../images/ew_z2_669_001.jpg"/>
         <div>
            <opener style="right">
               <choice><abbr>Sat</abbr><expan>Saturday</expan></choice><choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice> 
               <date when="1928-04-28"><choice><abbr>Apr</abbr><expan>April</expan></choice><choice><orig>.</orig><reg/></choice> 28<choice><orig>.</orig><reg>,</reg></choice>
                  <choice><abbr>'28</abbr><expan>1928</expan></choice><choice><orig>.</orig><reg/></choice></date>
            </opener>
            <opener>
               <salute>
                  Dear <name type="person">Eartha</name>,<lb/>
               </salute>
            </opener>
            <p style="indent">
               It is so sweet of you<lb/>
               to remember me in my<lb/>
               dreary hours of illness.<lb/>
            </p>
            <p style="indent">
               Yes, I really believe I'm<lb/>
               getting better, but my<lb/>
               recovery will be slow.<lb/>
               I shall perforce be denied<lb/>
               participation in all this<lb/>
               year's big events in <choice><orig>club-life</orig><reg>club life</reg></choice>,<lb/>
               politics, education, etc.<lb/>
               I must keep very quiet<lb/>
               and <hi style="underline">rest</hi>, <hi style="underline">rest</hi>, <hi style="underline">rest</hi>.<lb/>
            </p>
         </div>

         <note type="editorial">The following is the envelope included with the letter.</note>
         <div>
            <p>
               <stamp type="postmark">
                  <name type="place"><emph style="case(allcaps)">Tampa, <choice><abbr>Fla</abbr><expan>FL</expan></choice></emph>.</name>
                  <date when="1928-04-28"><emph style="case(allcaps)">Apr</emph><choice><orig/><reg>.</reg></choice>
                     28<choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice> 1928</date> 7 PM
               </stamp>
            </p>
            <p>
               Miss <name type="person">E. M. M. White</name><choice><orig>,</orig><reg/></choice><lb/>
               <name type="place" subtype="address">233 W. 1<hi style="superscript">st</hi>  St.</name>,<lb/>
               <name type="place" subtype="city">Jacksonville</name>,<lb/>
               <name type="place" subtype="state"><choice><abbr>Fla</abbr><expan>FL</expan></choice></name><choice><orig>.</orig><reg/></choice><lb/>  
            </p>
         </div>
         
         <pb n="2" facs= "../images/ew_z2_669_002.jpg"/>
         <div>
            <p>
               With all good wishes,<lb/>
               and sincere thanks for<lb/>
               your prayerful interest<lb/>
               in my welfare<choice><orig>,</orig><reg>.</reg></choice><lb/>
            </p>
            <closer style="right">
               <salute>
                  I am <choice><orig>Sincerely</orig><reg>sincerely</reg></choice> <choice><orig>Yours</orig><reg>yours</reg></choice><choice><orig/><reg>,</reg></choice><lb/>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">Blanche</name><lb/>
               </signed>
            </closer>
         </div>       
